      "content": "it's just so exhausting. the idea of \"rebuilding\" sounds like more work i don't have the energy for. it's like trying to rebuild a house that's already been burned to the ground. why would i want to keep dragging this empty version of myself around when that person is already gone? it would be so much easier to just... let it be over.",
